Also, next time you think you 'lekker' for using 'top' makeup brands. Someone else might be paying half the price for the same quality
Therefore check out the company, check out what brands they own. You might find a cheaper option, same quality
Eg, Coty owns both Calvin Klein and Rimmel. Huge difference in price. But most probably the same quality.
companies use the same/similar ingredients etc for their makeup brands but because there are different target markets, different pricing
Knowing your makeup brands, and the companies they are owned by, helps you ethically but also financially
